About VimCs
===========


Requirements
============
VimCs uses the RipGrep to function.

Installation
============
Set up a key binding as follows: nnoremap <leader>f :VimCs<CR>

Usage
=====
Start a search with :VimCs. Enter a search term, and press enter. You will then get a scratch buffer containing the search results.

Press enter while on a line to open the file at the given line in the current window. Press ctrl+t on a line to open it
in a new tab.

Press q to close the scratch buffer without opening anything.
